'''Fern<U+00E3>o Dias Pais''' (1608<U+2013>1681) or '''Fern<U+00E3>o Dias Pais Leme''' was a [[frontiersman]] from S<U+00E3>o Paulo.  He was known as the "Emerald Hunter" and was one of the most prominent [[bandeirante]]s together with [[Ant<U+00F4>nio Raposo Tavares]]. 

He is the great-great-grandfather of the Saint [[Frei Galv<U+00E3>o]].

